    <PackageId>NuStreamDocs.Icons.MaterialDesign</PackageId>
    <Description>Use any of the ~7000 Material Design Icons (MDI) in your NuStreamDocs documentation. Reference an icon as `:material-foo:` and the SVG is inlined directly into the page.</Description>
